commentary: Shakib Al Hasan to Hyatt, OUT Has that been caught at long-off? Hyatt hit the ball flat and hard towards long-off, Rubel Hossain came running in from the boundary and dived forward, catching it centimetres before it hit the turf. He stays motionless on the ground for a few moments before raising his finger, indicating it's out. The umpires refer it to the third umpire. It's a clean catch though, and Hyatt has to go. The delivery was tossed up slower and Hyatt didn't get to its pitch as he cleared his front foot to attack
shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Hyatt, OUT
text: Has that been caught at long-off? Hyatt hit the ball flat and hard towards long-off, Rubel Hossain came running in from the boundary and dived forward, catching it centimetres before it hit the turf. He stays motionless on the ground for a few moments before raising his finger, indicating it's out. The umpires refer it to the third umpire. It's a clean catch though, and Hyatt has to go. The delivery was tossed up slower and Hyatt didn't get to its pitch as he cleared his front foot to attack
